藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5c445cfd2af3859d7ffd745c9eef6a0f76b861be","tid":2089393,"uid":286513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力呀！游説！"},{"pid":"ce9c0fcd16c17f97103db8172c74ff2baf53015f","tid":2089393,"uid":23104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f0357a5ffbee54e8900bfbe6ca529dbc0d042e","tid":2089393,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db75b2809959eaefedee8ea2572f286428c99375","tid":2089393,"uid":23104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:55:53.000Z","msg":"叛國罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咱們中國不夠強大嗎 怎麼滾去拿外國藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這漢奸 還是個特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />nmsl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要求中國充共她財產  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:57:25.000Z","msg":"推下好喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class